lead_paragraph: Bradley Wiggins' hopes of leading Britain to team pursuit gold at the world track championships were foiled by old rivals Australia in a thrilling final on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Wiggins Denied as Australia Win Team Pursuit Gold
headline.main: Wiggins Denied as Australia Win Team Pursuit Gold
